Package: gtksourceview-sharp
Version: 2.0
Revision: 1028
Description: C# bindings for GTKSourceView
License: LGPL
Maintainer: Benjamin Reed <gtksourceview-sharp@fink.racoonfink.com>

Depends: gtk-sharp2 (>= 2.4.2-1022), gtksourceview-shlibs (>= 1.2-1), mono (>= 1.1.16-1), mono-tools (>= 1.1.11-1022)
BuildDepends: atk1 (>= 1.19.6-1), expat1, libpng3, cairo (>= 1.2-1), glitz, fontconfig2-dev (>= 2.3.2-13), freetype219 (>= 2.3.1-1), glib2-dev (>= 2.14.0-1), gtk+2-dev (>= 2.12.0-1), gtk-sharp2 (>= 2.4.2-1022), gtksourceview-dev (>= 1.2-1), libart2, libbonobo2-dev (>= 2.19.6-1), libgnomeprint2.2-dev (>= 2.18.0-1), libxml2, mono-dev (>= 1.1.14-1021), mono-tools (>= 1.1.11-1022), orbit2-dev (>= 2.14.8-1), pango1-xft2-ft219-dev (>= 1.17.5-1), pkgconfig (>= 0.21-1), x11-dev, xft2-dev

Source: http://go-mono.com/sources/%n-%v/%n-%v-0.10.tar.gz
Source-MD5: 2179634b8931e6be849a1e1f82c834e3

SetCPPFLAGS: -I%p/include
SetLIBS: -L%p/lib
SetMAKEFLAGS: -j1
NoSetCPPFLAGS: true
NoSetLDFLAGS: true
NoSetMAKEFLAGS: true
ConfigureParams: --mandir=%p/share/man --disable-dependency-tracking PKG_CONFIG_PATH="%p/lib/pango-ft219/lib/pkgconfig:%p/lib/fontconfig2/lib/pkgconfig:%p/lib/freetype219/lib/pkgconfig:$PKG_CONFIG_PATH" FREETYPE_CONFIG=%p/lib/freetype219/bin/freetype-config
CompileScript: <<
#!/bin/sh -ex

  export lt_cv_sys_max_cmd_len=65536
  perl -pi -e 's/hardcode_direct=yes/hardcode_direct=no/g' configure
  ./configure %c
  make
<<

InstallScript: <<
#!/bin/sh -ex

  export MONO_PATH="%i/lib:$MONO_PATH"
  make install DESTDIR=%d
  rm -rf %i/share/gtksourceview-1.0/language-specs
<<
DocFiles: AUTHORS COPYING* ChangeLog INSTALL NEWS README

PostInstScript:   [ -x "%p/bin/monodoc" ] && [ -d "%p/lib/monodoc" ] && "%p/bin/monodoc" --make-index >/dev/null 2>&1 || :

Homepage: http://go-mono.com/
DescDetail: <<
This package provides .NET assemblies that allow .NET / C#
programs to use the gtksourceview library.
<<

